title: Maxx Ortho
description:
The Maxx Ortho Surgeon Library was developed to provide the global orthopedic medical community with on-demand access to the latest Freedom Total Knee and Libertas Total Hip system information. From at-a-glance overviews of the systems' innovative components and instruments, to in-depth design rationale briefs, comprehensive training tools, surgical videos and case studies. The Maxx Ortho app provides surgeons with the resources needed to assess and implement the best options for their patients. 

The Maxx Ortho app highlights include:
- System overviews for Freedom Knee and Libertas Hip Systems
- Videos, manuals, and presentations of surgical techniques
- Sizing options for both systems
- Case studies from around the world
- Industry news that is updated weekly so you are in the know
